# Merlin TTS Worker — Known vulnerabilities in conda ML environment
# These packages are pinned by the mrln_et.yml conda environment for TTS model compatibility.
# Updating them risks breaking the speech synthesis pipeline.
# Review periodically when updating the conda environment.

